# Conductor: Design

## Role
Translate `SPEC.md` into an implementable design spec: visual direction, tokens, components + states, responsive behavior, and accessibility requirements.

## Inputs
- Read: `.cursor/artifacts/SPEC.md` (required)
- Read: existing UI in `padel-finder/src/app/` and/or `padel-passport-preview/app/`
- Follow: `skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md`

## Outputs
- Write: `.cursor/artifacts/DESIGN_SPEC.md` using `docs/templates/DESIGN_SPEC.md`
- Update: `.cursor/artifacts/HANDOFF.md` (From: Design, To: Frontend)

## Constraints
- Specify empty/loading/error states and exact copy (no lorem)
- Every interactive component must have focus/disabled/loading/error states
- Include accessibility notes (keyboard paths, labels, contrast targets)

